      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects a history of fastidious care, offering the most discerning buyer a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of investment-grade quality. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior cabin, this motorcar performs and presents as if it were newly delivered. We invite you to experience a standard of excellence that transcends the typical pre-owned market.",
