      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and drives like a dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
