    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a museum-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving powerhouse utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, both of which have been meticulously serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. Power is managed through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Crucially, the chassis has been future-proofed with proactive rear subframe reinforcement, and the rod bearings have been replaced to factory tolerances. With zero bushing deflection, a bone-dry undercarriage, and a perfectly dampened suspension, this M3 provides a surgical, analog driving experience. It is a rare, mechanically perfect example for the discerning collector who demands technical excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
