    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in its original, high-gloss factory paint, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dash is free of any UV damage, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. I have maintained a comprehensive binder of every service record since new, including a recent preventative fluid flush and a multi-point inspection that returned a perfect bill of health. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, with no signs of corrosion or leaks. This sale includes all original keys, the owner's manual set, and a clean title in hand. If you are looking for a turn-key, investment-quality example that requires zero excuses, this is the one.",
